STRYKER CORPORATION, dba Stryker Medical, et al., petitioners,
v.
HILL-ROM SERVICES, INC., et al. No. 14-358. Supreme Court of the United States Dec. 1, 2014.

Opinion

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Federal Circuit denied.

THE CHIEF JUSTICE took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
